{"tid":84047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【口裡說不】數據卻很誠實！ 中國客去年訪日創紀錄至637萬人次","createTime":"2017-01-17T08:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T08:55:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ff6f19b0effd476c301bcea2928d8b7b557b64","tid":84047,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"日本國家旅遊局公佈2016年訪日外國旅客人數估計數值，港人訪日人數按年升20.7%，全年達183.9萬人次；而網民經常排日的中國遊客，訪日人次亦達637.3萬，是訪日人次最多的國家，創遊日人次紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n日圓近年貶值不少，雖然口講排日，但中國人卻成為全球最喜歡到日本遊旅的國家，2016年的人數達637.3萬，較2015年的499.4萬人次，大幅增長27.6%，排第二的是韓國，按年升27.2%至509萬人次，台灣第三，按年升13.3%至416.7萬人次，愛遊日的港人亦按年升20.7%至183.9萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n日本駐港總領事館於去年10月，將香港到日本旅遊工作計劃簽證人數由每年250名增至1,500名，鼓勵港人到日本旅遊工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56184701&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56184701%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170117&d=78TSNX5xEDFVTFDYZLiyUaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=48bfcf8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56184701%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170117&h=b6c1de64\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56184701&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170117</a>"},{"pid":"31748d6a26acb2c91535a05ab031cb3ba0f68168","tid":84047,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}